body:
URF is the best mode in this game, I saw and still see alot of people quitting the game over the the toxic community (mainly) and some stupid system you guys made like the honor/ranked system, and yet, everytime URF is available, those people always come back just for that.
What you guys do? &quot;oh hey, I think it will be a great idea to bring Nexus Blitz (that no one cares) and put URF in it!&quot;
NOOOOO!!!! 
That&#039;s NOT gonna make people happy RIOT! You guys said URF would be back this month, and you put it in Nexus Blitz!? And u think that will be ok? come on... 
Even so URF is the best mode in game, and the only reason people quit and come back to game JUST to play that, you guys add URF in game like... once a year for like, 3 days or something.

Sometimes the game get&#039;s boring, URF is the best mode to make people have fun in game again and change the boring pace of things in game.

WE WANT URF!!!! BRING IT BACK PLEASE!!! (more often, for longest time!) {{sticker:sg-soraka}} {{sticker:sg-janna}} 
No one cares about Nexus Blitz, and that&#039;s gonna be there for at least a month...

PS: NOT ARURF, the REAL URF! {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
